    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "1. Overall"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "A service with the task of commanding the next active, highest priority chime event ID to the Chime Producer. The Chime Manager also provides a status of the chime subsystem to the functions within the vehicle that own chime events."
    },
